          <div style="font-weight:800;color:var(--pink);font-size:20px">Birthday Quiz</div>
          <div class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">12 funny Yes / No questions â€” see who knows Maiysha best!</div>

          <div style="margin-top:14px;display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center">
            <button class="secondary" id="restartBtn">Restart Quiz</button>
            <button class="secondary" id="showAnswersBtn">Show Answers</button>
